== Личная жизнь ==

Сонеджи имеет [[Индия|индийское]] корни, его родители проживают в городе [[Мумбаи]]. Работает страховым агентом<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uefa.com/footballeurope/news/kind=2/newsid=513931.html |title=Sonejee's Andorran odyssey |author=Lucy Turner |date=08.03.2007 |work= |publisher=UEFA.com |accessdate=2015-02-10 |lang=en}} ([http://web.archive.org/web/20100110031525/http://www.uefa.com/footballeurope/news/kind=2/newsid=513931.html Копия])</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/Sonejee-Masand-set-to-join-Churchill-Brothers/articleshow/5091754.cms |title=Sonejee Masand set to join Churchill Brothers |author=Marcus Mergulhao |date=06.10.2009 |work= |publisher=The Times of India |accessdate=2015-02-10 |lang=en}}</ref>.

